snippet.title: inCARceration - Gain parole by completing a series of strange and surreal jobs!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://crayonmelon.itch.io/incar?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt It's inCARceration -- a one of a kind warioware-style minigame collection!!!!!! 

You have been trapped in your car by an oppressive legal system (american) and your only hope of escape is to gain parole -- by completing a series of strange and surreal jobs!!!! 

Do you have what it takes to earn parole, or will you be executed for your failures?

➡️ More from Crayon https://crayonmelon.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
